            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/1b71663eba261362/text/000000241",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-1b71663eba261362-f09fcd twpub-1b71663eba261362-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 4.  Information about Donations to the Project Gutenberg\nLiterary Archive Foundation</h4></div>"
